lidation | T-004 (parallel with T-003) |\n| **T-006** | Migration -- delete hand-written code + update consumer import paths | T-005 |\n| **T-007** | Unit tests -- Scheme registration + Fake Client CRUD + Informer integration | T-006 |\n| **T-008** | Documentation + final validation | T-006 |\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_28529c375ffeE8nhSCaBnyHtSe","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Find AR-035 client-go info","time":{"start":1775882353798,"end":1775882487685}}}}
